query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS auto_targeting_performance (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  campaign_id VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  ad_group_id VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  targeting_type ENUM('close_match', 'loose_match', 'substitutes', 'complements') NOT NULL,
  date DATE NOT NULL,
  impressions INT DEFAULT 0,
  clicks INT DEFAULT 0,
  cost DECIMAL(10, 2) DEFAULT 0,
  sales DECIMAL(10, 2) DEFAULT 0,
  orders INT DEFAULT 0,
  units INT DEFAULT 0,
  acos DECIMAL(10, 4),
  roas DECIMAL(10, 4),
  ctr DECIMAL(10, 6),
  cvr DECIMAL(10, 6),
  cpc DECIMAL(10, 4),
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  UNIQUE KEY unique_perf (campaign_id, ad_group_id, targeting_type, date)
);
